    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = 0.36
    v0 = 0.02
    tmp = wp.sin(v1)
    v2 = (0.75 - wp.exp(wp.cos(tmp + 0.21)))
    tmp = v1
    v2 = (0.11 * wp.cos((tmp + 0.31 - v2 + 0.61)))
    tmp = (wp.cos(wp.exp(v1 + 0.72)) + (0.68 / (v0 + 0.18 / v0 + 0.39)))
    data[tid] = v0
